Source: live-foobillardplus
Section: games
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Ronny Standtke <ronny.standtke@fhnw.ch>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7)
Standards-Version: 3.7.3

Package: live-foobillardplus
Architecture: all
Depends: foobillardplus, live-resolution
Description: Starts foobillardplus with the current screen resolution
 This package enforces foobillardplus to start with the current screen resolution
 instead of the configured value. This way foobillard can easily be used on
 live systems without reconfiguration before every start.
